snippet.title: Shanye East's Quest To Burn To Death In Lava Secret % Walkthrough
snippet.description: This is a walkthrough on how to beat the secret % of Shanye version 15. This is not a speedrun, meaning that I am not using any of the speedrunning strats, including: Wall jumps and skipping parts of levels. If you want to play the game you can download it through this link https://mittens0407.itch.io/shanye-easts-quest-to-burn-to-death-in-lava My friend made this game, and he is also a semi-youtuber like me, so you should check out his channel. His name is Mittens0407, I'll try to pin his comment (if he does comment). This game is currently only played by my friends and I, and we're trying to expand the community right now, so it would mean a lot if you checked out the game for yourselves. We are also currently creating a wiki and we are trying to set up a speedrun.com category for this game. Thanks for watching and I hope you try Shanye out for yourselves.
